Box model:
Any delement in html is represented as Box
    - Border: Border is the fence line around the Box   
            border-width border-style border-color;
        for every border we can assign border-radius[corner radius]
            border-radius: size;
        We can specify border or border radius to only specific side
            border-left, border-rith, border-top, border-bottom,
            border-top-left-radius etc 

